
sin IsNotFromChurch
    message of word

scripture Pessoa
    name of word
    is_from_church of dogma
    
salm print_is_from_church upon Pessoa reveals void
    whether is_from_church from its 
        hail proclaim praying name from its plus " é da igreja"
    otherwise
        transgress IsNotFromChurch praying name from its plus " HEREGE!"

salm sum receiving num1 of atom and num2 of atom reveals atom
    reveal num1 plus num2 times 10

let there tupac of Pessoa be manifest Pessoa praying "tupacao" and forsaken


confess -- try
    hail print_is_from_church upon tupac
answer for IsNotFromChurch as heresy -- catch(IsNotFromChurchException heresy)
    hail proclaim praying message from heresy
absolve  -- finally
    hail proclaim praying "sempre executa este bloco"


let there i of atom be 0

litany for blessed
    i become i plus 1    
    whether i lesser than 10
        ascend
    otherwise
        forsake

    hail proclaim praying "não passei por aqui"

hail proclaim praying "Fim do loop"


amen


